{"tid":969023,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇由布院/別府有私人溫泉1泊2食推介下？","createTime":"2019-01-04T16:54:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T15:23:14.000Z","uid":32850,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"f20ea7d60794910c3f505d3fed5fc6cc99763420","tid":969023,"uid":32850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T16:54:02.000Z","msg":"3月中去<br />\n同爸媽&amp;女友<br />\n應該4人同房<br />\n有冇房入面有露天溫泉既一泊2食旅館推介下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者冇私人溫泉，但有貸切露天溫泉都ok<br />\n料理冇乜要求，溫泉旅館應該唔差得去邊<br />\n地點都冇所謂，因為自駕遊<br />\n但價錢想約$1500hkd以下1晚/每人<br />\n<br />\n睇左好多都幾貴下，都要$2000/一晚每人...<br />\n暫時只係搵左間叫御宿　由布乃庄都幾岩心水<br />\n有冇其他推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thx！"},{"pid":"aa7b6e54df63c020957afd5e1fe8f5529eb166c3","tid":969023,"uid":30708,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T17:11:28.000Z","msg":"4個人唔會好老尷？<br />\n你女友浸 又俾你老豆睇埋？<br />\n咁孝順㗎？"},{"pid":"1bc52dacfe5390eff3ee8d2f014c2a70537614ab","tid":969023,"uid":5393,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T06:50:23.000Z","msg":"古都花心旅館 <br />\n不過我未住過"},{"pid":"d50ea47c146e659319330b56ffeb94e3ced871c4","tid":969023,"uid":32850,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aa7b6e54df63c020957afd5e1fe8f5529eb166c3","tid":969023,"uid":30708,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T17:11:28.000Z","msg":"4個人唔會好老尷？<br />\n你女友浸 又俾你老豆睇埋？<br />\n咁孝順㗎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T11:45:49.000Z","msg":"所以想搵有貸切溫泉啊"},{"pid":"b317368e818825feda83174a74a97f18d5910d8e","tid":969023,"uid":63177,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T11:50:13.000Z","msg":"4人同房？<br />\n點解唔book2間 2人一間房"},{"pid":"1108e6f78f9c8ad640022c150c6e55d33884dd6e","tid":969023,"uid":32850,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa7b6e54df63c020957afd5e1fe8f5529eb166c3","tid":969023,"uid":30708,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-0